<body><div type="diplomatic"><pb facs="#facs_389" id="194r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"/>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content"><ab facs="#facs_389_r1l2">VVir ~ dıe <expan>Burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des <expan>R<ex>ats</ex></expan> der Stat cʒu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan> / <expan>Bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan> etc </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l3">daʒ für vns kumen ſind wılhelm Ebner vnd 
<del rend="strikethrough">Merkell Reck </del></ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l4">Markhart Reck vnſer <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> / vnd <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> vns fürgelegt </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l5">vvie ſıe gefangen worden weren vnd Jn etvvıeuil hab ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l6">nomen das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> heincʒ poſſeck hans poſſeck vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l7">aber hans poſſeck volhals genant hans von Grewſen </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l8">Nykel von Dölen hans Murr Michell hellwagen vnd </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l9">der ~ Beheim / dıe ſie der venknuſſe ledig gelaſſen vnd Jn </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l10">Jr hab <expan>wıdergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> daran ſıe wol benüg / als vns die </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l11"><expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan> ~ <expan>vnſ<ex>er</ex></expan> <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> geſagt / vnd gebeten <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> / daʒ vvir </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l12">darümb der ~ dıe hıe <expan>ob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> benant ſind freund werden </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l13">wolten / vnd alſo werden vvir <expan>derſelb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die hieuor ge = </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l14"><expan>ſchrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> ſten gut freund v̈mb die tat ongeuerde Mit </ab>
<ab facs="#facs_389_r1l15"><expan>vrk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicʒ brıefs <expan>v<ex>er</ex>ſ<ex>igelt</ex></expan> etc <expan>dat<ex>um</ex></expan> <expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> ııj̃ <expan>p<ex>oſt</ex></expan> Thome <expan>Ap<ex>oſto</ex>lı</expan> </ab>
</div>
</div><div type="regularised"><pb facs="#facs_389" id="194r"/><!--The following div is the container for the adress lines of the letter.-->
<div type="addressee"><ab/></div>
<!-- This div contains the letter itselfs. Additions to the text are contained in <add/> elements, struck text in <hi> elements with the attribute 'strikethrough' set to true. -->
<div type="content">
<ab>Wir, die <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> des <expan>r<ex>ats</ex></expan> der
                        stat czu <expan>Nür<ex>emberg</ex></expan>, <expan>bekenne<ex>n</ex></expan>
                        etc., daz für uns kumen sind Wilhelm Ebner und Markhart Reck, unser
                                <expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan>, und <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
                        uns fürgelegt, wie sie gefangen worden weren und in etwievil hab genomen;
                        das getan <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan> Heincz Posseck, Hans Posseck und
                        aber Hans Posseck, Volhals genant, Hans von Grewsen, Nykel von Dölen, Hans
                        Murr, Michell Hellwagen und der Beheim, die sie der venknusse ledig gelassen
                        und in ir hab <expan>widergeb<ex>e</ex>n</expan>
<expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daran sie wol benüg, als uns die
                                <expan>egen<ex>anten</ex></expan>
<expan>uns<ex>er</ex></expan>
<expan>burge<ex>r</ex></expan> gesagt und gebeten
                            <expan>hab<ex>e</ex>n</expan>, daz wir darümb der die hie
                                <expan>ob<ex>e</ex>n</expan> benant sind freund werden wolten; und
                        also werden wir <expan>derselb<ex>e</ex>n</expan> die hievor
                                ge<expan>schrib<ex>e</ex>n</expan> sten gut freund ümb die tat
                        ongeverde. Mit <expan>urk<ex>unde</ex></expan> dicz briefs
                                <expan>v<ex>er</ex>s<ex>igelt</ex></expan> etc.
                                <expan>Dat<ex>um</ex></expan>
<expan>fe<ex>ri</ex>a</expan> iii <expan>p<ex>ost</ex></expan> Thome
                                <expan>ap<ex>osto</ex>li</expan>.</ab>
</div>
</div></body>
